---
title: Ginger Beef Stir-Fry with Hoisin, Asparagus, and Basmati Rice
description: We’re welcoming back a HelloFresh classic! Tender beef and crisp asparagus are quickly stir-fried with warming ginger and served over fluffy basmati rice. Hoisin sauce adds a touch of sweetness and depth of flavor.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/56d5c4c14dab71137f8b4568.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/56d5c4c14dab71137f8b4568.pdf
